title.rendered: SUPREMA BIOENTRY W2 OUTDOOR IP FINGERPRINT DEVICE

content.rendered:
Suprema BioEntry W2 is a rugged fingerprint access control device featuring Suprema’s next generation biometric technology and security platform. BioEntry W2 provides class-leading performance and security by featuring Suprema’s latest fingerprint algorithm coupled by powerful quad-core CPU and LFD(live finger detection) technology.

Features

  • IP65, Dust & Waterproof
  • Power over Ethernet
  • TCP/IP, RS-485, Wiegand
  • 20 to 50 degrees operating temperature
  • Standalone RFID & Fingerprint Access Control
  • 2 internal inputs
  • 1 internal relay output
  • Suitable for outdoors
  • RF Option :MultiCLASS SE and Dual RFID (125kHz EM, HID Prox &13.56Mhz MIFARE, DESFire/EV1, FeliCa, iCLASS SE/SR, NFC, ISO14443A
